{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/linux2.md/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"2주차-linuxubuntu로-살아보기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-linuxubuntu%EB%A1%9C-%EC%82%B4%EC%95%84%EB%B3%B4%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"2주차 linuxubuntu로 살아보기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2주차 Linux(Ubuntu)로 살아보기</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d2bb74dcd8e0f6c2611d83a5ed054301/1fec9/1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.13513513513513%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/d2bb74dcd8e0f6c2611d83a5ed054301/fcda8/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d2bb74dcd8e0f6c2611d83a5ed054301/12f09/1.png 148w,\n/static/d2bb74dcd8e0f6c2611d83a5ed054301/e4a3f/1.png 295w,\n/static/d2bb74dcd8e0f6c2611d83a5ed054301/fcda8/1.png 590w,\n/static/d2bb74dcd8e0f6c2611d83a5ed054301/efc66/1.png 885w,\n/static/d2bb74dcd8e0f6c2611d83a5ed054301/c83ae/1.png 1180w,\n/static/d2bb74dcd8e0f6c2611d83a5ed054301/1fec9/1.png 3808w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>18.04버전의 화면 모습입니다. 알아보니 원래 Ubuntu는 'GNOME'이라는 데스크탑 환경을 채택했다가, 'Unity'환경으로 바꾸었었고, 이제 다시 18.04버전부터 'Unity'와 상당히 유사하게 디자인 된 테마를 달고 나온 'GNOME'이 다시 기본 데스크탑 환경으로 채택되었다고 합니다.</p>\n<p>기대했던 것보다 훨씬 깔끔하게 디자인되어 있는 것 같아서 나쁘지 않다는 생각을 했습니다. 하지만, 몇몇 프로그램을 시작해보면서 불편함을 느끼기 시작했습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/cdd12d289f5910433f3c859dd0ce1ae3/1fec9/2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.13513513513513%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"2\"\n        src=\"/static/cdd12d289f5910433f3c859dd0ce1ae3/fcda8/2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cdd12d289f5910433f3c859dd0ce1ae3/12f09/2.png 148w,\n/static/cdd12d289f5910433f3c859dd0ce1ae3/e4a3f/2.png 295w,\n/static/cdd12d289f5910433f3c859dd0ce1ae3/fcda8/2.png 590w,\n/static/cdd12d289f5910433f3c859dd0ce1ae3/efc66/2.png 885w,\n/static/cdd12d289f5910433f3c859dd0ce1ae3/c83ae/2.png 1180w,\n/static/cdd12d289f5910433f3c859dd0ce1ae3/1fec9/2.png 3808w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Ubuntu를 설치하고 가장 먼저 실행해본 것은 Firefox!</p>\n<p>뭔가 벌써 불편함이 느껴지지는 않으신가요?</p>\n<p>아마 불편함을 느꼈다면 저와 같은 생각이실겁니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6eb8cf05775bab63e5c388463a48b563/9c507/3_1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 14.864864864864865%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"3 1\"\n        title=\"3 1\"\n        src=\"/static/6eb8cf05775bab63e5c388463a48b563/fcda8/3_1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6eb8cf05775bab63e5c388463a48b563/12f09/3_1.png 148w,\n/static/6eb8cf05775bab63e5c388463a48b563/e4a3f/3_1.png 295w,\n/static/6eb8cf05775bab63e5c388463a48b563/fcda8/3_1.png 590w,\n/static/6eb8cf05775bab63e5c388463a48b563/efc66/3_1.png 885w,\n/static/6eb8cf05775bab63e5c388463a48b563/c83ae/3_1.png 1180w,\n/static/6eb8cf05775bab63e5c388463a48b563/9c507/3_1.png 2768w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>안그래도 좌측의 런처(Launcher)때문에 작업 화면이 손해를 보고 있는데, 상단바 때문에 상당히 큰 공간이 낭비되고 있다는게 보이시나요?</p>\n<p>심지어 메뉴바도 활성화되지 않은 상태입니다. 만약 메뉴바가 활성화되어있었다면 더 큰 공간을 차지하게 되는 것이죠.</p>\n<p>인터넷을 뒤져보니 이런 불편함을 호소하는 사람들은 저뿐만이 아니었고, 해결 방법을 어렵지 않게 찾을 수 있었습니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"1-top-bar-제거하기---unite\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-top-bar-%EC%A0%9C%EA%B1%B0%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0---unite\" aria-label=\"1 top bar 제거하기   unite permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Top Bar 제거하기 - Unite</h3>\n<p>우선 <a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/ko/firefox/addon/gnome-shell-integration/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://addons.mozilla.org/ko/firefox/addon/gnome-shell-integration/</a>에 들어가서 Add-On을 설치해줍니다.</p>\n<p>그 후, 바탕화면에서 우클릭 후 'Open Terminal'로 Terminal을 엽니다</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/80b4cda637a094f82a29e3c0b889bcfd/1fec9/4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.13513513513513%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"4\"\n        title=\"4\"\n        src=\"/static/80b4cda637a094f82a29e3c0b889bcfd/fcda8/4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/80b4cda637a094f82a29e3c0b889bcfd/12f09/4.png 148w,\n/static/80b4cda637a094f82a29e3c0b889bcfd/e4a3f/4.png 295w,\n/static/80b4cda637a094f82a29e3c0b889bcfd/fcda8/4.png 590w,\n/static/80b4cda637a094f82a29e3c0b889bcfd/efc66/4.png 885w,\n/static/80b4cda637a094f82a29e3c0b889bcfd/c83ae/4.png 1180w,\n/static/80b4cda637a094f82a29e3c0b889bcfd/1fec9/4.png 3808w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>위와 같이 Terminal이 열렸다면 다음처럼 입력해줍니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ sudo apt-get install chrome-gnome-shell</code></pre></div>\n<p>이제 Unite를 설치해주어야 하는데, Unite는 패키지 의존성이 있기 때문에 터미널에 다음과 같이 입력해서 패키지를 먼저 설치해줍니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ sudo apt install x11-utils gnome-shell-extension-dashtodock</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3d3c786311da4735ff67c12fe4685b54/1fec9/5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.13513513513513%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"5\"\n        title=\"5\"\n        src=\"/static/3d3c786311da4735ff67c12fe4685b54/fcda8/5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3d3c786311da4735ff67c12fe4685b54/12f09/5.png 148w,\n/static/3d3c786311da4735ff67c12fe4685b54/e4a3f/5.png 295w,\n/static/3d3c786311da4735ff67c12fe4685b54/fcda8/5.png 590w,\n/static/3d3c786311da4735ff67c12fe4685b54/efc66/5.png 885w,\n/static/3d3c786311da4735ff67c12fe4685b54/c83ae/5.png 1180w,\n/static/3d3c786311da4735ff67c12fe4685b54/1fec9/5.png 3808w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>이제 Unite plugin을 설치해줄 차례입니다!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://extensions.gnome.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://extensions.gnome.org/</a></p>\n<p>위 링크에 접속해줍니다. 그 후, Unite를 검색해서 설치해주면 됩니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/cfc01c1beb85f907c851638fd9116ee1/1fec9/6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.13513513513513%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"6\"\n        title=\"6\"\n        src=\"/static/cfc01c1beb85f907c851638fd9116ee1/fcda8/6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cfc01c1beb85f907c851638fd9116ee1/12f09/6.png 148w,\n/static/cfc01c1beb85f907c851638fd9116ee1/e4a3f/6.png 295w,\n/static/cfc01c1beb85f907c851638fd9116ee1/fcda8/6.png 590w,\n/static/cfc01c1beb85f907c851638fd9116ee1/efc66/6.png 885w,\n/static/cfc01c1beb85f907c851638fd9116ee1/c83ae/6.png 1180w,\n/static/cfc01c1beb85f907c851638fd9116ee1/1fec9/6.png 3808w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Unite를 눌러 들어가준 뒤, 아래 사진의 표시한 부분을 클릭하여 On으로 만들어줍니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/157dc1071f1c75d8539906ed83d69290/1fec9/7.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.13513513513513%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"7\"\n        title=\"7\"\n        src=\"/static/157dc1071f1c75d8539906ed83d69290/fcda8/7.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/157dc1071f1c75d8539906ed83d69290/12f09/7.png 148w,\n/static/157dc1071f1c75d8539906ed83d69290/e4a3f/7.png 295w,\n/static/157dc1071f1c75d8539906ed83d69290/fcda8/7.png 590w,\n/static/157dc1071f1c75d8539906ed83d69290/efc66/7.png 885w,\n/static/157dc1071f1c75d8539906ed83d69290/c83ae/7.png 1180w,\n/static/157dc1071f1c75d8539906ed83d69290/1fec9/7.png 3808w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>설치할 것이냐고 묻는 팝업창이 뜨고, 여기서 Install을 선택하게 되면,</p>\n<p>다음과 같이 Top Bar와 Title Bar, Menu Bar가 공간을 같이 사용하면서 차지하는 공간이 줄어들게 됩니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/24f96545267a176c0eee2d8dd0f23e5a/1fec9/8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.13513513513513%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"8\"\n        title=\"8\"\n        src=\"/static/24f96545267a176c0eee2d8dd0f23e5a/fcda8/8.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/24f96545267a176c0eee2d8dd0f23e5a/12f09/8.png 148w,\n/static/24f96545267a176c0eee2d8dd0f23e5a/e4a3f/8.png 295w,\n/static/24f96545267a176c0eee2d8dd0f23e5a/fcda8/8.png 590w,\n/static/24f96545267a176c0eee2d8dd0f23e5a/efc66/8.png 885w,\n/static/24f96545267a176c0eee2d8dd0f23e5a/c83ae/8.png 1180w,\n/static/24f96545267a176c0eee2d8dd0f23e5a/1fec9/8.png 3808w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>어떤 차이인지 비교해볼까요?</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/12c22a479017d1cc78856706717e3d85/1fec9/9.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.13513513513513%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"9\"\n        title=\"9\"\n        src=\"/static/12c22a479017d1cc78856706717e3d85/fcda8/9.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/12c22a479017d1cc78856706717e3d85/12f09/9.png 148w,\n/static/12c22a479017d1cc78856706717e3d85/e4a3f/9.png 295w,\n/static/12c22a479017d1cc78856706717e3d85/fcda8/9.png 590w,\n/static/12c22a479017d1cc78856706717e3d85/efc66/9.png 885w,\n/static/12c22a479017d1cc78856706717e3d85/c83ae/9.png 1180w,\n/static/12c22a479017d1cc78856706717e3d85/1fec9/9.png 3808w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>왼쪽에 있는 창이 Unite를 설치한 후의 모습이고, 오른쪽에 있는 창이 Unite를 설치하기 전의 모습입니다.</p>\n<p>실질적으로는 Title Bar 크기 만큼의 공간이 확보가 된 것인데, 이정도 크기 확보로도 전보다는 훨씬 시원시원한 느낌이 드는 것 같습니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-sleepmode-방지---caffeine\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-sleepmode-%EB%B0%A9%EC%A7%80---caffeine\" aria-label=\"2 sleepmode 방지   caffeine permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. SleepMode 방지 - Caffeine</h3>\n<p>Ubuntu를 사용하다 보니, Ubuntu를 실행시키고 이것저것 검색하거나 글을 쓰다 들어오면,</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/11dd4f72e42d26d6a64af874c9ad6319/1fec9/10.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.13513513513513%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"10\"\n        title=\"10\"\n        src=\"/static/11dd4f72e42d26d6a64af874c9ad6319/fcda8/10.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/11dd4f72e42d26d6a64af874c9ad6319/12f09/10.png 148w,\n/static/11dd4f72e42d26d6a64af874c9ad6319/e4a3f/10.png 295w,\n/static/11dd4f72e42d26d6a64af874c9ad6319/fcda8/10.png 590w,\n/static/11dd4f72e42d26d6a64af874c9ad6319/efc66/10.png 885w,\n/static/11dd4f72e42d26d6a64af874c9ad6319/c83ae/10.png 1180w,\n/static/11dd4f72e42d26d6a64af874c9ad6319/1fec9/10.png 3808w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>어느 순간 이렇게 위처럼 SleepMode가 되어 잠겨버리고 다시 로그인해야하는 상황이 종종 있었습니다.</p>\n<p>이게 또 생각보다 거슬릴 때가 많아서 방법을 모색하던 중, extension 설치를 통해 해결할 수 있다는 사실을 알았습니다.</p>\n<p>그 extension의 이름이 바로 Caffeine입니다. </p>\n<p>Ubuntu를 잠들지 못하게 하겠다는 의지가 담긴 이름같습니다. <del>정말 이름한번 잘 지은 것 같습니다.</del></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/32ec58518e7405039555257d246ef2f3/7f7f8/11_1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70.27027027027026%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"11 1\"\n        title=\"11 1\"\n        src=\"/static/32ec58518e7405039555257d246ef2f3/fcda8/11_1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/32ec58518e7405039555257d246ef2f3/12f09/11_1.png 148w,\n/static/32ec58518e7405039555257d246ef2f3/e4a3f/11_1.png 295w,\n/static/32ec58518e7405039555257d246ef2f3/fcda8/11_1.png 590w,\n/static/32ec58518e7405039555257d246ef2f3/efc66/11_1.png 885w,\n/static/32ec58518e7405039555257d246ef2f3/c83ae/11_1.png 1180w,\n/static/32ec58518e7405039555257d246ef2f3/7f7f8/11_1.png 2396w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Ubuntu Software에서 우측 상단의 검색 버튼을 눌러 'Caffeine'을 검색한 후, 설치를 진행합니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2105609a0b53fede00d6e1dbdf68e7f4/cc40b/12.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 12.837837837837837%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAfUlEQVQI122OzQ6CMBCEef+XIyZyMFESQLpd29I/PQ/tClEjh8m3O5PMbpNTAtOM/nIGKYX+dsXiLPzi/hSDR4pBmFMEM+E+jSWzxffiNzXQakZ3aqGJMI1DoZKZ9Vt1Nw/+KaysR5w1274V7qE1Rj57PbNcP9J32c6PH4Qr3sfiVac1cqkAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"12\"\n        title=\"12\"\n        src=\"/static/2105609a0b53fede00d6e1dbdf68e7f4/fcda8/12.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2105609a0b53fede00d6e1dbdf68e7f4/12f09/12.png 148w,\n/static/2105609a0b53fede00d6e1dbdf68e7f4/e4a3f/12.png 295w,\n/static/2105609a0b53fede00d6e1dbdf68e7f4/fcda8/12.png 590w,\n/static/2105609a0b53fede00d6e1dbdf68e7f4/efc66/12.png 885w,\n/static/2105609a0b53fede00d6e1dbdf68e7f4/c83ae/12.png 1180w,\n/static/2105609a0b53fede00d6e1dbdf68e7f4/cc40b/12.png 2394w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>설치가 완료된후, Caffeine을 실행시키게 되면 우측 상단에 컵 모양 아이콘이 생기게 됩니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 312px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a3b5191921ef630fbf75b5575e378ddb/17474/13.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 18.91891891891892%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"13\"\n        title=\"13\"\n        src=\"/static/a3b5191921ef630fbf75b5575e378ddb/17474/13.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a3b5191921ef630fbf75b5575e378ddb/12f09/13.png 148w,\n/static/a3b5191921ef630fbf75b5575e378ddb/e4a3f/13.png 295w,\n/static/a3b5191921ef630fbf75b5575e378ddb/17474/13.png 312w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 312px) 100vw, 312px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>이 아이콘을 클릭한 후 'Activate'를 선택하게 되면,</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 470px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ba75c482b8bced74a5e2c3d495032e22/f96db/14.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 82.43243243243244%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"14\"\n        title=\"14\"\n        src=\"/static/ba75c482b8bced74a5e2c3d495032e22/f96db/14.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ba75c482b8bced74a5e2c3d495032e22/12f09/14.png 148w,\n/static/ba75c482b8bced74a5e2c3d495032e22/e4a3f/14.png 295w,\n/static/ba75c482b8bced74a5e2c3d495032e22/f96db/14.png 470w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 470px) 100vw, 470px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>다음과 같이 컵에서 김이 올라오며 실행된 것을 볼 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 302px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/856cff9744e276b27ebcd6b08f4f2404/5f1d2/15.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 18.91891891891892%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"15\"\n        title=\"15\"\n        src=\"/static/856cff9744e276b27ebcd6b08f4f2404/5f1d2/15.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/856cff9744e276b27ebcd6b08f4f2404/12f09/15.png 148w,\n/static/856cff9744e276b27ebcd6b08f4f2404/e4a3f/15.png 295w,\n/static/856cff9744e276b27ebcd6b08f4f2404/5f1d2/15.png 302w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 302px) 100vw, 302px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>이렇게 실행해 두면 Ubuntu를 가만히 두더라도 SleepMode가 실행되지 않는 것을 확인했습니다</p>\n<p>더 이상 귀찮게 암호를 다시 입력해서 잠금을 해제해야하는 일이 생기지 않겠네요ㅎㅎ</p>\n<h2 id=\"느낀-점\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%8A%90%EB%82%80-%EC%A0%90\" aria-label=\"느낀 점 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>느낀 점</h2>\n<p>Ubuntu를 사용해보면서, 정말 많은 사람들이 함께 만들어가고 있다는 느낌을 받았습니다.</p>\n<p>무언가 사용하다 불편한 점이 있다고 한다면 인터넷 서칭을 하다보면 비슷한 불편함을 겪었던 사람들을 찾을 수 있고, 해결책 또한 쉽게 찾을 수 있다는 것이 정말 마음에 들었습니다.</p>\n<p>누군가 불편함을 느끼면 그것을 해결하기 위해 다함께 노력하고, 공유하는 그 시스템을 보고, 몸소 느끼면서 Linux의 매력을 알 수 있었던 한주였습니다.</p>\n<p>'Firefox 브라우저 디자인이 보기 안좋다! 이렇게 수정했으면 좋겠다'라는 의견이 있으면 그 문제를 해결하는 방법을 찾아내고 서로 공유했기에 제가 이렇게 쉽고 빠르게 해결 방안을 찾고 문제를 해결할 수 있었고,</p>\n<p>마찬가지로 'Ubuntu가 SleepMode에 들어가지 않았으면 좋겠다!'라는 의견이 있으면 그 문제를 해결하는 소프트웨어를 만들어내고 공유해서 많은 사람들이 쓸 수 있도록 했기 때문에 저는 간단하게 그 소프트웨어를 내려받음으로써 불편함을 해소할 수 있었습니다.</p>\n<p>이렇게 잘 구축된 운영체제와 커뮤니티가 서로 맞물려 상호작용하면서 긍정적인 작용을 하고있는 것을 느낄 수 있었습니다.</p>\n<p>Linux의 어찌보면 가장 두드러지는 특징이라고 할 수 있는 '오픈소스 소프트웨어'를 직접 체험해보고 몸소 장점을 느껴봤다는 점에서 의미있는 시간이었다고 생각합니다.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>이번주는 Ubuntu를 사용하면서 불편한 점을 해소하는 방법을 알아봤다면,</p>\n<p>다음주부터는 간단한 코딩을 Ubuntu를 통해 해보거나 다른 응용프로그램들을 설치해서 직접 사용해보는 활동들을 주로 해보도록 하겠습니다.</p>","excerpt":"2주차 Linux(Ubuntu)로 살아보기  18.04버전의 화면 모습입니다. 알아보니 원래 Ubuntu는 'GNOME'이라는 데스크탑 환경을 채택했다가, 'Unity'환경으로 바꾸었었고, 이제 다시 18.04버전부터 'Unity…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/linux2.md/#2%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-linuxubuntu%EB%A1%9C-%EC%82%B4%EC%95%84%EB%B3%B4%EA%B8%B0\">2주차 Linux(Ubuntu)로 살아보기</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/linux2.md/#1-top-bar-%EC%A0%9C%EA%B1%B0%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0---unite\">1. Top Bar 제거하기 - Unite</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/linux2.md/#2-sleepmode-%EB%B0%A9%EC%A7%80---caffeine\">2. SleepMode 방지 - Caffeine</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/linux2.md/#%EB%8A%90%EB%82%80-%EC%A0%90\">느낀 점</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/linux2.md/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Linux(Ubuntu)로 살아보기 (2) - Unite, Caffeine","date":"Mar 29, 2020","tags":["Linux(Ubuntu)"],"keywords":["Linux","Ubuntu","Parallels","Software"],"update":"Jan 01, 0001"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/linux2.md/","series":[],"lastmod":"0001-01-01"}}}